cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper deals with the problem of domain adaptation in medical imaging, specifically for MRI organ segmentation. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms and transfer learning, which are relevant to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The task of organ segmentation is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and the use of reverse classification accuracy (RCA) involves the evaluation of model performance, which is relevant to the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
